data.title: Chico Hamilton Quintet
data.text:
This article is about the album recorded in 1956. For the album recorded in 1955, see Chico Hamilton Quintet featuring Buddy Collette.

Chico Hamilton Quintet is a live album by drummer and bandleader Chico Hamilton, released on the Pacific Jazz label.[1][2]

Reception

[edit]

Professional ratingsReview scoresSourceRatingAllMusic[3]

AllMusic rated the album 3 stars.[3]
